00:19:16.540 --> 00:19:18.590
Here they certainly will match.

00:19:18.590 --> 00:19:22.340
So here's the rule for
block multiplication,

00:19:22.340 --> 00:19:28.880
that if this has
blocks like, A --

00:19:28.880 --> 00:19:34.220
so maybe A1, A2, A3,
