00:33:15.090 --> 00:33:18.080
So I can get anything.

00:33:18.080 --> 00:33:19.860
Now, let me see, what do I mean?

00:33:19.860 --> 00:33:21.880
How I going to
computer A inverse?

00:33:21.880 --> 00:33:24.060
So A inverse --

00:33:24.060 --> 00:33:28.360
here's A inverse, now,
